          <ul class="text-sm text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 space-y-1">
            <li>Use consistent header toolbar layout across panels</li>
            <li>Group related fields into labeled sections</li>
            <li>Provide clear pagination when records exceed one</li>
            <li>Use "Allow Edit" checkboxes for field-level permissions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-red-200 dark:border-red-900/50 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20">
